These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, disco, electronic, house
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of house##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco | hip-hop | house |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat, frog, horse
1. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | chinchilla | frog | rat | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, camping, dancing, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | dancing | magic-tricks | camping | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, helicopter, train
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | helicopter | boat | quad-bike | train |

 #################################

 
